165
00:12:00,399 --> 00:12:01,519
Did Jiang Kele discover it?

166
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,639
You can't come here anymore.

167
00:12:05,719 --> 00:12:06,680
If you get caught,

168
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:07,920
